\ntwo-dimensional one. We provide experiments with real images showing the good\nperformance of the technique.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Mar 2012 13:18:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jan 2014 23:55:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-21"}
